<br>Found in tribes throughout the world
<br><br>
<br>A feral, cannibalistic sub race of humans that live in loosely formed tribes. 
<br>Escaped tortured humans from southern continent years ago became these  
<br>These twisted creatures where formally humans, enslaved and tortured for centuries. They lost all sense of humanity and became known, in common, as the Kín.
